\id ACT - Kunbarlang Acts 1:8-11 - 23-11-23
\h Acts
\toc1 Acts
\toc2 Acts
\toc3 ACT
\mt1 Acts
\c 1
\s1 God kapundjarrkrdam Jesus
\s2 Jesus la ngayi katakapurrk warrenj katadjarnganj korro Olive kuntulk kadjanganj korro mantulum.
\p 
\v 8 Jesus kaputumarnayngurnta ngayi katakapurrkwarranj “God kanyanynilaka nayi nakukin kimalng kanyanjka birnukutbe. La kanyutuwunj rdulkarra. Ngorro ngunjdjitaka djirripunmernanjngunjdje kirtimarrk ngunjdjitanyolyolme ngayi. Korro yalbi Jerusalem la Judea pingadju kuyi yalbi la ngemek Samaria, la ngemek ngunjdjitaka kunbarrabarrkiddbe yalbi korro djarre. Yiwanj ngayi ngudjdjitanyolyolme.”
\p 
\v 9 Yiwanj babi kuyi Jesus kapuddumarnayngurndda ngob God kapundjarrkrdam kapunkanginj korro kaddum. La ngayi kaddakapurrk warrenj munguy kaddarddukirdanj kaddarnay kuyi kakirdanj kaddum. Yiwanj kuyunu kanganjkirtanj kapunparrkpum nayi Jesus bonj ngorro la ngayi kaddakapurrkwarrenj ngurndda kiddarnani.
\v 10 Yiwanj beddbebonj munguy kaddarddukirddanj kaddum. Yiwanj kirnddabonj bidju kapurrk kirddimarrk kabarrardayinj manburrba nayi kawalarrbunj kaddakaburrkdjanganj kirnddabonj.
\v 11 Benengkabonj kabarrangurndda, “Nuwuddbe kirddimarrk nguddukang Galilee. Bardda rnungu nguddudja kendda munguy nguddurduka kaddum. God kabunkanginj nayi Jesus korro kaddum. La yiwanj kanyanywonj bonjbonj korro nguddurnay kakirddanj kaddum balkime, yiwanj bapi kanyanjbakdjuwa kunbonjbonj. 
